    "The percentage usage of each type of interaction was as follows: Head Movement (20%), Point and Click (16%), Gamepad locomotion (17%), Room Scale (10%), and Teleport locomotion (37%).",
    "Figure 14 displays the percentage usage of each type of interaction on the Y-axis, and the types of iVR experience on the X-axis.",
